Installation Instructions
=========================

The CernVM-FS build system uses cmake.  In order to compile and
install, run from the source directory

    mkdir -p build
    cd build
    cmake ../
    make
    sudo make install

In order to build the unit tests in addition, use
`cmake -DBUILD_UNITTESTS=yes ../`

For more details, please see the [technical report](http://cernvm.cern.ch/portal/filesystem/techinformation).

